(firstQuint)Study of Two Dose Levels of RTA 402 in Patients With Advanced Malignant Melanoma.

 This is a phase II, open label, randomized study in patients with unresectable Stage III or Stage IV malignant melanoma.

 Patients will be randomly assigned to two different doses of RTA 402 administered orally once daily for 28 consecutive days, for up to 18 months.

